We are searching for a ** Brisbane-based candidate ** to work in our Banyo
Northside office.

The successful new Full Stack Developer with Ammonite will complete the
following duties in the position:

  * Team player that mentors colleagues and reviews code to ensure quality is maintained. 
  * Develop front and back-end applications. 
  * Design efficient and intuitive user experiences. 
  * Writing code across the full application stack with a focus on quality. 
  * Strong customer service skills and ability to liaise with customers to discuss technical issues. 
  * Additional duties to be discussed. 

##  Role Requirements:

To be successful in this position a combination of the following will be
required:

  * 4 + years’ experience in a similar role. 
  * Experienced in estimating, designing and managing projects. 
  * Experienced with MySQL. 
  * PHP, JavaScript, SQL, HTML, CSS. 
  * Experience with AWS. 
  * Back-end web application experience in PHP. 
  * Experience in modern front-end frameworks and JavaScript libraries. 
  * Troubleshooting, debugging and issue resolution skills. 
  * Experience with Git version control. 
  * Experience with Linux valuable but not necessary. 
  * Team player that can lead daily Agile work practice. 
  * You have a growth mindset, embracing challenges to continuously improve and innovate. 

##  Who we are:

Ammonite has proudly developed a completely integrated Learning Management
System, Student Management System and Training Management System that enables
our customers to deliver world-class learning to their students in the
Vocational Education Training (VET) environment. We are constantly researching
and engaging in the world’s best practices and leading-edge approaches as we
strive for ways to deliver better training for our students. Feedback from our
customers is that we are truly revolutionising the way training is being
delivered to the VET market for over 10 years.

By joining Ammonite, you will be with an organisation that is well-regarded
for the innovative approach we have taken as well as our commitment and
passion to the industry. We proudly try to meet "world's best practice" levels
in everything we do, including our recent changes to incorporate ChatGTP into
our platform.

